## рҹҡҖ Kurulum ve ГҮalДұЕҹtДұrma (DetaylДұ)

### Gereksinimler

| Gereksinim | Versiyon | Zorunlu mu? |
|------------|----------|:-----------:|
| **Python** | 3.11+ | вң… Evet |
| **Git** | 2.x | вң… Evet |
| **pip** | 23+ | вң… Evet |
| **FFmpeg** | 4.x | вҡ пёҸ Opsiyonel (video/audio) |
| **Playwright** | latest | вҡ пёҸ Opsiyonel (HyperFrames) |
| **Docker** | 20+ | вҡ пёҸ Opsiyonel (Container Sandbox) |

### AdДұm AdДұm Kurulum

#### 1. Repoyu Klonla

```bash
git clone https://github.com/recaiozil-wq/reymen-agean.git
cd reymen-agean
```

#### 2. Sanal Ortam OluЕҹtur

```bash
# Python 3.11+ sanal ortam
python -m venv .venv

# AktifleЕҹtir
# Linux/macOS:
source .venv/bin/activate

# Windows (CMD):
.venv\Scripts\activate

# Windows (PowerShell):
.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1

# Windows (Git Bash):
source .venv/Scripts/activate
```

#### 3. BaДҹДұmlДұlДұklarДұ YГјkle

```bash
# Temel baДҹДұmlДұlДұklar
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Alternatif: Editable install (geliЕҹtirme modu)
pip install -e .

# TГјm opsiyonel baДҹДұmlДұlДұklar dahil (Г¶nerilir)
pip install -e ".[full]"

# GeliЕҹtirme araГ§larДұ dahil
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# TГјmГј
pip install -e ".[full,dev]"
```

#### 4. API AnahtarlarДұnДұ Ayarla

```bash
# Г–rnek .env dosyasДұnДұ kopyala
cp config/.env.example .env

# .env dosyasДұnДұ dГјzenle вҖ” en az bir LLM API key'i girmelisin
# Г–nerilen: DEEPSEEK_API_KEY (en ucuz ve hДұzlДұ)
nano .env   # veya notepad .env (Windows)
```

`.env` dosyasДұnda ayarlanmasДұ gereken temel deДҹiЕҹkenler:

```bash
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here        # Zorunlu (veya baЕҹka bir LLM)
PASA38_BOT_TOKEN=your-bot-token          # Telegram bot 1
REYMEN_BOT_TOKEN=your-reymen-bot-token   # Telegram bot 2
KIRAL38_BOT_TOKEN=your-kiral38-bot-token # Telegram bot 3
REYMEN_JWT_SECRET=your-secret-32chars    # Web UI iГ§in JWT gizli anahtarДұ
```

#### 5. (Opsiyonel) FFmpeg Kurulumu

```bash
# Windows (winget)
winget install ffmpeg

# Windows (Chocolatey)
choco install ffmpeg

# Linux (Debian/Ubuntu)
sudo apt install ffmpeg

# macOS (Homebrew)
brew install ffmpeg

# DoДҹrulama
ffmpeg -version
```

#### 6. (Opsiyonel) Playwright Kurulumu

```bash
# Playwright'Дұ yГјkle
pip install playwright

# Chromium tarayДұcДұsДұnДұ indir
playwright install chromium
```

#### 7. (Opsiyonel) Docker Kurulumu

Container Sandbox Г¶zelliДҹi iГ§in Docker gereklidir:

```bash
# Docker'Дұ kur (https://docs.docker.com/get-docker/)
docker --version

# Docker Compose'u doДҹrula
docker compose version
```

#### 8. ГҮalДұЕҹtДұr

```bash
# DoДҹrudan Г§alДұЕҹtДұr (interaktif REPL)
python reymen_launcher.py

# Tek seferlik soru
python reymen_launcher.py -z "Merhaba, nasДұlsДұn?"

# Versiyon bilgisi
python reymen_launcher.py --version

# YardДұm
python reymen_launcher.py --help
```

### Docker ile Kurulum

```bash
# Docker ile Г§alДұЕҹtДұr (proje kГ¶kГјnde)
docker compose up

# Arka planda Г§alДұЕҹtДұr
docker compose up -d

# LoglarДұ izle
docker compose logs -f
```

### ReYMeN'i TanДұ

ReYMeN framework'ГјnГј tanДұmak iГ§in Г¶rnek script'leri Г§alДұЕҹtДұrabilirsin:

```bash
# Merhaba ReYMeN вҖ” temel kullanДұm
python examples/00_merhaba_reymen.py

# Plugin kullanДұmДұ
python examples/01_plugin_kullanimi.py

# Container Sandbox
python examples/03_container_sandbox.py

# MCP Server baЕҹlat
python -c "from src.gateways.mcp_server import main; main()"
```

### SДұk KarЕҹДұlaЕҹДұlan Hatalar

| Hata | OlasДұ Sebep | ГҮГ¶zГјm |
|------|-------------|-------|
| `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'src'` | Sanal ortam aktif deДҹil | Sanal ortamДұ aktifleЕҹtir: `source .venv/bin/activate` |
| `openai.AuthenticationError` | API key yanlДұЕҹ/eksik | `.env` dosyasДұnda `DEEPSEEK_API_KEY` deДҹerini kontrol et |
| `python-telegram-bot` hatasДұ | Telegram bot token'Дұ geГ§ersiz | `@BotFather`'dan token'Дұ yenile |
| `FFmpeg not found` | FFmpeg kurulu deДҹil | YukarДұdaki FFmpeg kurulum adДұmlarДұnДұ uygula |
| `Playwright` hatasДұ | TarayДұcДұ binary'si eksik | `playwright install chromium` Г§alДұЕҹtДұr |
| `docker: command not found` | Docker kurulu deДҹil | Docker Desktop'Дұ kur (Windows/macOS) veya `apt install docker.io` (Linux) |
| `Permission denied` | Dosya izinleri | `.env` ve `config/config.yaml` dosyalarДұnДұn okunabilir olduДҹunu kontrol et |
| `sqlite3.OperationalError` | VeritabanДұ kilitli | `.ReYMeN/` dizinindeki `.db` dosyalarДұnДұ sil ve yeniden baЕҹlat |

### Platform FarklДұlДұklarДұ

| Д°Еҹlem | Linux/macOS | Windows |
|-------|-------------|---------|
| **Sanal ortam aktifleЕҹtirme** | `source .venv/bin/activate` | `.venv\Scripts\activate` |
| **.env kopyalama** | `cp config/.env.example .env` | `copy config\.env.example .env` |
| **FFmpeg kurulumu** | `apt install ffmpeg` / `brew install ffmpeg` | `winget install ffmpeg` |
| **Yol ayracДұ** | `/` | `\` (veya `/` Git Bash'te) |
| **Ortam deДҹiЕҹkeni** | `export VAR=value` | `set VAR=value` (CMD) / `$env:VAR='value'` (PowerShell) |

> рҹ’Ў **Д°pucu:** Windows'ta **Git Bash** kullanmanДұz Г¶nerilir вҖ” Linux benzeri komutlar ve yol formatДұ saДҹlar.

