## вңЁ Key Features

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| рҹ§  **Reasoning Core** | **Ornith-1.0**: Error вҶ’ `DURUM_OKU()` вҶ’ solution вҶ’ `analytics.db`. Closed learning loop that improves over time |
| рҹ‘Ҙ **3 Bots, One Center** | `pasa_38`, `ReYMeN`, `kiral38` share config/memory/sessions via **`durum.json`** (single source of truth) |
| рҹ§© **Plugin System** | 7 lifecycle hooks: `on_load`, `on_message`, `pre_llm_call`, `post_llm_call`, `on_session_start/end`, `on_unload` |
| рҹ”— **MCP Server** | Self-hosted MCP with 6 tools: `list_sessions`, `send_message`, `search_sessions`, `get_session`, `run_code`, `get_status` |
| рҹ”‘ **Provider Abstraction** | 5+ providers: DeepSeek, OpenAI, Anthropic, xAI, OpenRouter. Switch providers in **one line of config** |
| вң… **Pydantic Validation** | Type-safe tool calls with automatic JSON repair |
| рҹ“Ҡ **OpenTelemetry** | LLM/tool/session spans with token, cost, and latency tracking |
| рҹҗі **Container Sandbox** | Docker isolation (off/partial/full) for secure code execution |
| рҹ“Һ **@file / @url Reference** | Inline reading via `@file:config/config.yaml` or `@url:https://...` |
| рҹ”Ҡ **Voice Mode** | Real-time voice conversation (TTS + STT) |
| рҹ©ә **Self-Healing** | 8 proactive checks: config drift, watchdog, SOUL sync, state.db pruning, weekly reports |
| рҹ”„ **Auto Startup** | 3 bots start headlessly on reboot (VBS) |
| рҹҢҗ **17+ Platforms** | Telegram, Discord, WhatsApp, Slack, Teams, Matrix, Signal, Mattermost, DingTalk, Feishu, WeCom, Google Chat, Home Assistant, BlueBubbles, QQ Bot, Yuanbao, and more |
| рҹ—ғпёҸ **FTS5 Session Search** | Full-text search across all sessions with auto-logging |
| рҹ”„ **Self-Update** | `reymen update --check/--auto` for seamless upgrades |
| рҹ“Ұ **Memory Compaction** | 50K conversation limit with auto-archive and LRU cache cleanup |
| рҹ“ң **Rules Engine** | 5 categories, 6 built-in rules вҖ” every action is validated |
| рҹҸ—пёҸ **Sub-agent Delegation** | `ThreadPoolExecutor`-based parallel task execution |
| рҹ”җ **JWT Auth System** | Multi-user authentication with access + refresh tokens |
| рҹ”Җ **Framework Adapters** | Optional LangGraph / CrewAI / AutoGen compatibility layer |
| рҹ–јпёҸ **Web UI Image Gen** | GET/POST `/image-gen` endpoint, 5 providers |
| рҹ”„ **A2A Messaging** | Agent-to-Agent message broker with thread-safe queues |
| рҹҺ® **CLI / TUI** | Rich terminal interface with status bars, spinners, and progress indicators |

