## рҹ“Ӯ Directory Structure

```
src/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ reymen/                  # Framework core
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ cereyan/            # Brain, Motor, Conversation Loop
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ beyin.py        # рҹ§  Reasoning engine
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ motor.py        # вҡҷпёҸ Action executor
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ conversation_loop.py  # рҹ”„ Bot conversation loop
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ session_search.py     # рҹ”Қ FTS5 search
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ memory_compaction.py  # рҹ’ҫ Memory management
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ once_hafiza.py        # рҹ§  Confidence-based learning
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ proaktif_kontrol.py   # рҹ©ә Proactive maintenance
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ arac/               # Tools (50+)
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tool_registry.py
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ tool_executor.py
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ framework_adaptor.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ plugin/             # PluginBase + PluginManager
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ plugins/            # User plugins
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ hafiza/             # Session DB, OnceHafiza, Vector Memory
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ guvenlik/           # Container Sandbox, File Safety, Auth
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ sistem/             # Credential Persistence, DB Config
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ web_ui/             # FastAPI web interface
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ tools/              # Obsidian, HyperFrames, Delegation
в”ңв”Җв”Җ gateways/               # Platform integrations
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ discord_bot.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ telegram_bot.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ mcp_server.py
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ platforms/          # 17+ platform adapters
в”ңв”Җв”Җ core/                   # Reasoning Core, Credential Pool
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ observability.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ credential_pool.py
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ provider_abstraction.py
examples/                   # 4 usage scenarios
tests/                      # 112 test files
```

